CMORlight, DKRZ, V7, 2017, Hans Ramthun


1. please checkout the source code from DKRZ gitlab: https://gitlab.dkrz.de/k204081/CMORlight

Command: 'git clone https://gitlab.dkrz.de/k204081/CMORlight -b master'

or development branch with 'git clone https://gitlab.dkrz.de/k204081/CMORlight -b hansdev'



2. run Buildout

- wget -O bootstrap.py https://bootstrap.pypa.io/bootstrap-buildout.py

- set python path and make sure that all needed packages are installed: numpy,netCDF4

- run 'python bootstrap.py' which creates bin/buildout

- run 'bin/buildout'



3. installation in the system

- for the istallation in the system run 'python setup.py install'

- in case of errors or missing packages please install them with pip or othe installers



When ready check program with: 'python cmorlight.py -h' or the new version with 'python cmorlight2.py -h'

